{% endif %}| **{{ i18n.syllabus.labels.semester }}** | {{ course.semester }} |
| **{{ i18n.syllabus.labels.ects }}** | {{ course.ects }} |
| **{{ i18n.syllabus.labels.language }}** | {{ course.language | upper }} |
| **{{ i18n.syllabus.labels.institution }}** | {{ course.organization.institution }} |
| **{{ i18n.syllabus.labels.department }}** | {{ course.organization.department }} |

## {{ i18n.syllabus.instructors }}

{% for inst in course.instructors %}
- **{{ inst.name }}**{% if inst.role is defined %} ({{ inst.role }}){% endif %}{% if inst.email is defined %} — {{ inst.email }}{% endif %}

